<div class="p_r3_04" id="part_2">
	<div class="p_left">
	<!-- left begin -->
	<div class="w_01" id="block_m_8">
			<h2 class="w_title">
				<span class="w_name">关键物品：砥柱铭</span>
				<span class="w_more"></span>
			</h2>
			<div class="w_cont"><div class="w_cont_bg">
				<!-- content begin -->
				<div class="w_cont_box">
<div id="cont_m_8_box" class="contBox"><div class="c_p_04" id="cont_m_8">

<div class="c_pic">
<a href="http://finance.sina.com.cn/money/collection/zgsh/20100721/13388337223.shtml" target="_blank"><img src="http://i3.sinaimg.cn/cj/2010/0721/S16162T1279693026293.jpg" alt="黄庭坚《砥柱铭》" /></a>
<p><a href="http://finance.sina.com.cn/money/collection/zgsh/20100721/13388337223.shtml" target="_blank">黄庭坚《砥柱铭》</a></p>
<div class="memo">黄庭坚《砥柱铭》，行书。此卷长八米，抄录唐代魏征《砥柱铭》，全文六百多字。黄庭坚大字行书凝练有力，结构独特，是北宋书坛杰出的代表，与苏轼、米芾、蔡襄并称“宋四家”。</div>
</div>

</div></div>
</div>
				<!-- content end -->
			</div></div>
			<div class="w_bot"><div class="w_bot_bg"></div></div>
		</div>
	<!-- left end -->
	</div>
	<div class="p_middle">
	<!-- middle begin -->
	<div class="w_01" id="block_m_9">
			<h2 class="w_title">
				<span class="w_name">关键人物：傅申</span>
				<span class="w_more"></span>
			</h2>
			<div class="w_cont"><div class="w_cont_bg">
				<!-- content begin -->
